                        <p class="case-block-text-subtext short-length">Not everyone is motivated by numbers, and it&rsquo;s hard to quantify happiness. So we created a challenge-based model that provides qualitative feedback on top of users&rsquo; stats.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="inner-block two-third float-left">
                        <img class="case-block-image maintain-size align-right" src="../images/genz/coaches.svg" data-sr="enter left, move 200px">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <!-- END case-block -->

            <section class="case-block top-padded genz-off-white">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="inner-block one-third absolute-left vertical-center mobile-padded-below">
                        <h2 class="case-block-text-heading short-length">Attention to detail from every side</h2>
                        <p class="case-block-text-subtext short-length">We ensured that mentors also feel at home in the interface and catered to their interests with relevant statistics and a custom scheduler. </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="inner-block two-third float-right relative">
                        <img class="case-block-image" src="../images/genz/card-container.svg">
                        <img class="case-block-image absolute" src="../images/genz/card-1.svg" data-sr="enter bottom, move 200px">
                        <img class="case-block-image absolute" src="../images/genz/card-2.svg" data-sr="wait .25s, enter bottom, move 200px">
                        <img class="case-block-image absolute" src="../images/genz/card-3.svg" data-sr="wait .5s, enter bottom, move 200px">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <!-- END case-block -->

            <section class="case-block case-full-image genz-laptop"></section>
            <!-- END case-block -->

            <section class="case-block genz-off-white mobile-container">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="inner-block one-third absolute-left vertical-center mobile-padded-below">
                        <h2 class="case-block-text-heading short-length">Skimming by cards</h2>
                        <p class="case-block-text-subtext short-length">The interface uses cards as an organization tool to improve skimmability. Users can quickly sort through information presented to them.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="inner-block two-third float-right" data-sr="enter right, move 200px">
                        <img class="case-block-image" src="../images/genz/stats.svg">
                    </div>
                </div>

            </section>
            <!-- END case-block -->

            <section class="case-block genz-red">
                <div class="container">
                    <img class="case-block-text-quote-icon" src="../images/genz/quote.svg" data-sr="enter top, move 75px">
                    <p class="case-block-text-quote align-center">&ldquo;The Brave team brings an impressive depth of knowledge and experience to the table. Each time we met, they presented excellent work and had inspiring ideas and insights to contribute. They were invaluable partners every step of the way.‚Äù&rdquo;</p>
                    <p class="case-block-text-citation align-center">Doug Anderson, <em>Founder, Gen Z Connect</em></p>
                </div>
            </section>
            <!-- END case-block -->

